    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until softened</p><p>Tip: Watch the garlic like a hawk to make sure it doesn’t burn!</p>",
