        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>with your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>curry powder </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>with your<strong> soy sauce </strong>and<strong> half </strong>your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[75ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil, then cook for 1-2 min or until thickened</p>",
