    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, drain and add your <strong>king prawns</strong></p><p>Cook for 6-7 min or until cooked through – these are your <strong>Singapore-style king prawns</strong></p><p>Once cooked through, set aside until the rice is ready</p>",
