    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, return the pan with the prawns to a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with your <strong>blanched peas </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 1 min or until the peas are warmed through</p><p>Mix until fully combined</p>",
