      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy king prawn & egg Singapore-style fried rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>and the<strong> remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
